OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782910144
OL,3,CTrump took in over $1 billion from
OL,4,Ccrypto in first year back in office
OL,6,FForbes estimates Trump's net worth at
OL,7,F$6 billion (around #4.5 billion), up
OL,8,Ffrom $2.3 billion (#1.7 billion) in
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FTrump took in tens of millions in fees
OL,12,Ffrom a flurry of new hotel, resort and
OL,13,Fcondo deals overseas that amounts to
OL,14,Fthe biggest property expansion ever in
OL,15,Fthe century since the family business
OL,16,Fwas founded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
