PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782910144
OL,3,CTrump took in over $1 billion from
OL,4,Ccrypto in first year back in office
OL,6,FMany of those countries were
OL,7,Fnegotiating with the US over tariffs,
OL,8,Fmilitary aid and other important
OL,9,Fmatters while the family business was
OL,10,Fstriking the deals.
OL,12,FA property in the United Arab Emirates
OL,13,Fgenerated $10.4 million (around #7.8
OL,14,Fmillion) for the Trump business last
OL,15,Fyear, meanwhile, one in Saudi Arabia
OL,16,Fbeing built by a real estate developer
OL,17,Fclose to the ruling family sent the
OL,18,Fpresident's company $9 million (around
OL,19,F#6.8 million).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
