FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782910144
OL,3,CTrump took in over $1 billion from
OL,4,Ccrypto in first year back in office
OL,6,FOne of his prominent domestic
OL,7,Fproperties, Mar-a-Lago in Florida,
OL,8,Fnotched big growth last year, too.
OL,10,FTrump took in $77 million (around #58
OL,11,Fmillion) from the property, a 50% jump
OL,12,Ffrom the year earlier when he was just
OL,13,Fanother citizen, as heads of state and
OL,14,Fbusinesspeople flocked to it in his
OL,15,Fnew term.
OL,17,FThe disclosure report doesn't give
OL,18,Fprofit figures, just revenue, so it's
OL,19,Fimpossible to know how much he is
OL,20,Fearning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
