OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782910144
OL,3,CTrump took in over $1 billion from
OL,4,Ccrypto in first year back in office
OL,6,FThe billionaire, Justin Sun, has
OL,7,Frepeatedly denied his spending on
OL,8,FTrump businesses had anything to do
OL,9,Fwith his federal case, while World
OL,10,FLiberty has dismissed the notion of a
OL,11,Fconflict of interest.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, investors have seen the
OL,14,Fvalue of their Trump-tied holdings
OL,15,Fdrop significantly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
