PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782910144
OL,3,CTrump took in over $1 billion from
OL,4,Ccrypto in first year back in office
OL,6,FThe price of World Liberty tokens has
OL,7,Ffallen 80% since they started trading
OL,8,Fin September. And the Trump souvenir
OL,9,Fcoins that spiked to more than $74
OL,10,F(#55.89) in the days after launching
OL,11,Fin January 2025 now sell for $1.68
OL,12,F(#1.27).
OL,14,FThe White House has repeatedly said
OL,15,FTrump put his business in a trust
OL,16,Fmanaged by his sons and is not
OL,17,Finvolved in its decisions and that
OL,18,Fthere are no ethics issues to discuss.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
