OL,3,CTrump took in over $1 billion from
OL,4,Ccrypto in first year back in office
OL,6,F"Neither the President nor his family
OL,7,Fhas ever engaged ` or will ever engage
OL,8,F` in conflicts of interest,"
OL,9,Fspokeswoman Anna Kelly said.
OL,11,F"All actions by President Trump and
OL,12,Fhis administration are taken in the
OL,13,Fbest interest of the American people."
